{"tid":1658833,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"打氣對於手足好重要","createTime":"2019-10-16T15:41:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T15:46:29.000Z","uid":39268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"92a5610642b5bf493ab0796e4fca54832040eb9c","tid":1658833,"uid":39268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:41:56.000Z","msg":"每次經過連儂牆見到手足喺度痴文宣，有好多都係學生/情侣，戴住口罩默默耕耘。又或者中學生集會喺度默站/組人鏈，都希望大家可以講聲加油，唔好俾孤單籠罩住佢哋。<br />\n雖知道大家可能趕時間，但一句唔該都好緊要，你哋知唔係係夜晚喺人少嘅地方痴文宣其實都有壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGaRPgQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGaRPgQ.jpg&h=88f1684a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkeGr3w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkeGr3w.jpg&h=a4c122c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D2DcyJx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD2DcyJx.jpg&h=ae88450e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9bb8a44d3a3ce731eda1470e728f99f016991684","tid":1658833,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:42:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人可唔可以爭爭氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日美國眾議院通過香港民主人權法案<br />\n你當撚人condom咩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通過左就唔駛多謝人？<br />\n仲有呀！<br />\n條Bill 未過參議院架！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好咁老定！<br />\n唔該去twitter多謝人地支持，<br />\n然後講香港真係好需要條Bill啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkg